Module openj9.dtfj
Package com.ibm.dtfj.corereaders.j9

Class J9RASFragmentJ6v2

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.dtfj.corereaders.j9.J9RASFragmentJ6v2
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    J9RASFragment
    public class J9RASFragmentJ6v2
extends Object
implements J9RASFragment
    Represents the J9RAS structure starting from Java 6 SR09 which contains the DDR blob pointer Java 6 32 bit : length = 0x248, version = 0x20000 TID+PID+DDR Java 6 64 bit : length = 0x280, version = 0x20000 TID+PID+DDR
